11 COMMITTEE SUBSTITUTE
12 A Joint Resolution approving certain Oklahoma Medical
Marijuana Authority proposed major rule changes; and
13 directing distribution.
14
15
16 WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
17 Statutes, the Oklahoma State Legislature shall adopt a separate
18 joint resolution to approve or disapprove major rules.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
20 AND THE SENATE OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
21 SECTION 1. The Legislature hereby approves the following
22 proposed major rule changes submitted by the Oklahoma Medical
23 Marijuana Authority on or before February 1, 2026: OAC 442:10-1-9;
24 442:10-1-9.1; 442:10-2-1; 442:10-2-2; 442:10-2-4; 442:10-2-6;
